        <h2 class="left-heading destination-section-heading">Zakynthos / Zante Town</h2>
        <p>After arriving in the island's main city of Zakynthos (Zante Town) you might like to hike up the hill to the <strong>Bochali View Point</strong>, which offers excellent views over the coast.</p>
        <p>The viewpoint is approximately 1.6 miles (2.6 km) one way from the ferry departure point, and 1.2 miles (1.9 km) back to the Zakinthos Bus Station, where you can take the bus to other towns around the island.</p>
    </section>


