        <p>Continue up the coast to the Plakaki Rocks, where you can take in striking views of the surrounding white cliffs with a very short walk from the parking area. If you're making good time you might stop next at <strong>Korakonissi</strong>, a strange but beautiful formation along the coast.</p>
